{"tid":1918586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(重要的事) 日副首相麻生︰「武漢病毒」名稱才正確","createTime":"2020-03-10T07:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T09:00:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d3a01d39a074923ef4f5245df49f5f265d014349","tid":1918586,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/10/phprtRTfo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F10%2FphprtRTfo.jpg&h=64f3151d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（取自山田宏推特）<br />\n<br />\n日本自民黨參議員山田宏在國會質詢時以「武漢肺炎」稱呼中國武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒肺炎，雖在日本引起爭議，但日本副總理大臣兼財務大臣麻生太郎今天在內閣會議後記者會中，也直呼為「武漢病毒」。他表示，發生在武漢的病毒被冠上了「新型」等名稱，不過他認為「武漢病毒」才是正確的稱法。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情擴大，造成金融市場混亂，日本有人將它稱為「可樂納衝擊」（Corona shock），擔心市場災情直逼2008年的「雷曼衝擊」（Lehman shock），麻生指出，雷曼兄弟破產造成的全球金融危機是發生於金融機關，市場缺乏現金，但這次情況不同，他不認為會觸發另一波新的金融危機，希望各界冷靜應對。<br />\n<br />\n對於日本政府針對武漢肺炎提出的第二波緊急對策，各界對於追加經濟對策充滿期待，麻生則表示，追加經濟對策必須視「武漢病毒」疫情受到控制後才能確定，目前的經濟還沒糟到必須採取緊急對策的階段。<br />\n<br />\n自民黨參議員山田宏使用「武漢肺炎」名稱在參院預算委員會中提出質詢，質詢影片在推特上被大量轉發點閱超過221萬次，很多日本網友稱鑽他有guts，不畏中國壓力，但前東京都知事舛添要一卻在電視新聞節目中提出公開批判，認為山田宏的歧視性用語無法解決任何問題，日本必須和中國合作一起對抗疫情。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿龐皮歐日前連2天在接受媒體訪問談到新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）時，也頻頻以「武漢病毒」或「武漢肺炎」來稱呼，中國外交部發言人耿爽以「我們譴責這種卑劣做法」表達中方強烈不滿。麻生似乎也不甩中國跳腳，今天使用「武漢病毒」的稱呼，山田宏則在他的推特貼文說「不愧是麻生大臣，直言不諱」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3094878\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3094878&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=03ac36de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3094878&h=99981718\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3094878</a>"},{"pid":"697ba85c22b73718ebd1d84d5b5b32fd859344fc","tid":1918586,"uid":68556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:55:08.000Z","msg":"中國武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa04a501983e6d2261aafa8806ef7c2c4668b24","tid":1918586,"uid":287269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:08:58.000Z","msg":"係時候係國際線正名武漢肺炎 connect 美日同全球"},{"pid":"8a8e7c67916e887ffbe4336ba2217b1f45885ae8","tid":1918586,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/yamazogaikuzo/status/1237225172911845376?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyamazogaikuzo%2Fstatus%2F1237225172911845376%3Fs%3D20&d=m5cPLj0qQ3YL0oTVN36eSgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=fd051869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyamazogaikuzo%2Fstatus%2F1237225172911845376%3Fs%3D20&h=50742faf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/yamazogaikuzo/status/1237225172911845376?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"f603e984b1e395510f96989ab1ae2c4ee099000f","tid":1918586,"uid":342786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:35:47.000Z","msg":"日本新型肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4ce30b14c2ca44381f58d047f83865f4324f3f","tid":1918586,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T09:00:37.000Z","msg":"正解"}]}